{"tid":154110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全國政協原副主席受賄　判囚終身","createTime":"2017-03-13T05:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T07:23:45.000Z","uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1d299ceb04e4287e772329ac2e595eb9f273b6","tid":154110,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全國政協原副主席蘇榮<br />\n受賄1.16億判囚終身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2017年1月23日 時事脈搏</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/01/23/1479235_fdd4ea57ce484403cbec59b189f5b746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2F1479235_fdd4ea57ce484403cbec59b189f5b746.jpg&h=fd10c68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國政協原副主席蘇榮案今午一審宣判，蘇榮數罪並罰被判處無期徒刑，剝奪政治權利終身，並處沒收個人全部財產。審理查明，蘇榮收受財物價值1.16億元(人民幣‧下同)。<br />\n<br />\n山東省濟南市中級人民法院對蘇榮受賄、濫用職權、巨額財產來源不明案一審公開宣判，對被告人蘇榮以受賄罪判處無期徒刑，剝奪政治權利終身，並處沒收個人全部財產；以濫用職權罪判處有期徒刑七年；以巨額財產來源不明罪判處有期徒刑七年，決定執行無期徒刑，剝奪政治權利終身，並處沒收個人全部財產。<br />\n<br />\n蘇榮當庭表示服從法院判決，不上訴。<br />\n<br />\n經審理查明，於2002年至2014年，蘇榮利用職務上的便利，為他人在企業經營、職務晉升調整等事項上謀取利益，本人直接或通過他人收受相關單位和個人財物合共折合1.16億餘元；濫用職權，致使公共財產、國家和人民利益遭受重大損失；蘇榮對共計折合8027萬餘元的財產不能說明來源。<br />\n<br />\n濟南市中級人民法院認為，蘇榮已構成受賄罪、濫用職權罪、巨額財產來源不明罪，均應依法懲處並數罪並罰。鑒於蘇榮到案後如實供述自己的罪行，主動交代辦案機關尚未掌握的部分受賄犯罪事實；認罪悔罪，贓款贓物已全部追繳，具有法定、酌定從輕處罰情節，依法可對其從輕處罰。法庭遂作出上述判決。"},{"pid":"a031c7f5f31ef05269542c662f4d0446f387c7d3","tid":154110,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-min.jpg&h=fec872d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上台坐低之後個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431f081638c3cc5dfb62aeddb7b2404016d3b342","tid":154110,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-min.jpg&h=fec872d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上台坐低之後個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔放佢上呢個位, 習大大點可以直接搞鳩佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53377d9ed83f5ced9f1dbc17ae0ebf75c297e1e0","tid":154110,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-min.jpg&h=fec872d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上台坐低之後個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔放佢上呢個位, 習大大點可以直接搞鳩佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果真係咁搞，燒山究竟算唔算燈返佢落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YHR5MOYg_eU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYHR5MOYg_eU&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7046cad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YHR5MOYg_eU</a>"},{"pid":"4a30fecbaaa43ad28a2efb959d1d12b22b7ac1cc","tid":154110,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.martinoei.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E6%94%BF%E5%8D%94%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.martinoei.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-min.jpg&h=fec872d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上台坐低之後個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔放佢上呢個位, 習大大點可以直接搞鳩佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都傻，睇下今日新聞啦。<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權對上面陽奉陰違，今日就坐監；689愛黨愛國愛港，做政協副主席。<br />\n<br />\n都借班港區政協放哂風，689可以做政協副主席的原因：對國家安全有貢獻。"}]}